==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Duykerbok
<hw>Duy"ker*bok</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[D.
<ets>duiker</ets> diver + <ets>bok</ets> a buck, lit., diver buck. So
named from its habit of diving suddenly into the bush.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A small South African antelope (<spn>Cephalous
mergens</spn>); -- called also <altname>impoon</altname>, and
<altname>deloo</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Duyoung</ent>⟦br⟧
